name: INQUISITION_GENESIS #01
description:
This is the first piece of a series called INQUISITION, it’s also my first cryptoart ever: it has never been published anywhere else and was painted with the purpose of becoming an OBJKT, this is xcasstle’s true henesis.

There are 4 basic ways to interpret art: first reaction, content, historical context, and personal context. Each method of understanding is less important than the way in which they connect with each other. Art is constantly morphing, but some people just don’t get it, it doesn’t matter if they’re young or old, progressive or conservative, artists or not.
